textline.data: The system shall inform the crew using a Led by turning it on for 60 second
The system shall read the value from pressure sensor
The system shall check if the threshold = 20 bar
The system shall inform the crew about the high pressure
The system shall check the high pressure in the cabin
The system shall protect the crew aganist high pressure
